00:39:28.930 --> 00:39:30.410
NOELLE SELIN: Yes.

00:39:30.410 --> 00:39:33.480
So in the mercury
negotiations, there

00:39:33.480 --> 00:39:36.990
was a lot done-- so a lot of the
nongovernmental organizations

00:39:36.990 --> 00:39:38.870
have banded together
internationally

00:39:38.870 --> 00:39:41.400
