01:20:39.240 --> 01:20:44.550
and try to frame it in a
more concrete discussion.

01:20:44.550 --> 01:20:48.450
So what are we going to do
with everything we've learned.

01:20:48.450 --> 01:20:50.390
You're going to
eventually want to make--

01:20:50.390 --> 01:20:52.280
drive a change in a company.

01:20:52.280 --> 01:20:54.710
How should I start with
all these inventions,

01:20:54.710 --> 01:20:58.410
the technical side, now the
political side, the NGO side,

01:20:58.410 --> 01:21:01.660
the complexity of the networking
